data.description: 1.25 Acres, 4 bay shop, 2 car garage plus spacious home and Privacy!  BBQ and entertain year round in the log gazebo while enjoying the peaceful sounds of the creek below bordering the property. Territorial views of Big Beef canyon. Featuring 2,332 Sq Ft home, 3 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms, Cozy Wood stove, efficient Heating/Cooling with newer ductless mini splits. Charming rounded brick stairway accents the knotty pine walls. Huge kitchen boasts Italian granite countertops, sit up island & updated appliances. Primary suite with two balconies, dual sinks and walk in closet. New roof, trusses & attic. Lake Symington amenities. Excellent location with convenient access to Silverdale, shopping & bases. You will love coming home!
